<h2 id="_short_description">Short description</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>These template functions and template variables can only be used to configure the layout of email templates. Find out more about email templates <a href="/en/crm/sending-emails#1200">here</a>.</p>
